{"tid":2078848,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律師會：指定法官損司法獨立","createTime":"2020-06-25T10:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T11:44:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a3773920e3890d28179873c9f473d2a53131ca","tid":2078848,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:54:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200625/L3FQGIFIVVI7JDKW75FKKROFXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2FL3FQGIFIVVI7JDKW75FKKROFXI%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfbCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=223b3e72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2FL3FQGIFIVVI7JDKW75FKKROFXI%2F&h=0a56e5bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200625/L3FQGIFIVVI7JDKW75FKKROFXI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n律師會：指定法官損司法獨立<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/C-ZRW_696zxVd5bLrIAsiMfa5pM=/973x674/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DKPKR7QT337E5W6UNPU6MQXMHA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FC-ZRW_696zxVd5bLrIAsiMfa5pM%3D%2F973x674%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDKPKR7QT337E5W6UNPU6MQXMHA.gif&h=c50b891b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n律師會昨發表聲明對港版國安法表達憂慮；圖為會長彭韻僖。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥前日稱由特首指定法官審理國安案件，做法不罕見，並嘲諷反對者「孤陋寡聞」。不過，繼大律師公會表達憂慮後，連作風保守的律師會昨日亦發出聲明，關注指定法官程序會損害司法獨立，並強調特首應該根據司法人員推薦委員會的建議作出任命。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：多人致電查詢打爆熱線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n憂送中疑犯失人權保障<br />\n<br />\n律師會昨日發稿強調，司法獨立是香港作為一個普通法司法管轄區的司法制度重要基石，不容削弱。律師會表示，關注指定法官程序，賦予特首監察和影響司法機構的權力，公。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n內<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n。的司法程序管轄，令人質疑公平審訊權等基本人權是否可以獲得保障，希望當局盡快澄清。<br />\n<br />\n律師會又指，若然當局在過程中能夠諮詢各個持份者，相信可以增加<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n訂，並符合一國兩制的方針。律師會兩星期前曾經發表聲明，對國安法提出七項建議，包括罪行必須沒有追溯力、公開審訊、不應篩選外國法官等。"},{"pid":"1d82ecebed768d0de3ec96e76b1a2d7071f1f0ac","tid":2078848,"uid":53003,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"親帝制派的律師會都咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117823e456d883989e8dc0f028e59a7bbde7e22a","tid":2078848,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d82ecebed768d0de3ec96e76b1a2d7071f1f0ac","tid":2078848,"uid":53003,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"親帝制派的律師會都咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:24:55.000Z","msg":"何君僥呢隻賤人<br />\n唔係做過會長咩<br />\n仲咩唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe4d40cd51b50671aeb960425e2a8af6cb7c3ee","tid":2078848,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:30:44.000Z","msg":"有冇英文版，想share 比外國記者"},{"pid":"4cdb02e2cd09a99511d76aa578b3bae999ad45ba","tid":2078848,"uid":42340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦<br />\n<br />\n成班垃圾<br />\n依家呀特首中2點就點呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲係到吠吠吠"},{"pid":"4aa03c768fd0d672d670c78bd324fc9e83e1843d","tid":2078848,"uid":45358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:35:19.000Z","msg":"有感覺好快就spin去：冇指定法官=黨安法冇問題"},{"pid":"ddd791edc6db0973d2230b4ddf4ec792e5ec4e7e","tid":2078848,"uid":28432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1d82ecebed768d0de3ec96e76b1a2d7071f1f0ac","tid":2078848,"uid":53003,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"親帝制派的律師會都咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"香港司法大陸化 香港律師地位只會愈黎愈低光環好快冇晒<br />\n為自己利益為自尊點都會出下聲既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5060524001e8b63c4f802e